@Löwen.Api_HostAddress = https://localhost:7197/api/Payment
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### Add payment
POST {{Löwen.Api_HostAddress}}/add-payment
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "orderId": "b5b3a1e8-91ab-4d6c-981a-6e612ccf0455",
  "amount": 250.00,
  "paymentMethod": "CreditCard",
  "transactionId": "txn_123456789",
  "status": "Pending"
}

###

### Get payment by ID
GET {{Löwen.Api_HostAddress}}/get-payment-by-id?id=b5b3a1e8-91ab-4d6c-981a-6e612ccf0455
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get payments by order
GET {{Löwen.Api_HostAddress}}/get-payments-by-order?orderId=4eeb9e61-9ff1-4b65-8121-1c5a3cb6d3a1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Update payment status
PUT {{Löwen.Api_HostAddress}}/update-payment-status/b5b3a1e8-91ab-4d6c-981a-6e612ccf0455,Completed
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
